  "description": "介绍康奈尔大学的公私合营模式、土地赠与传统、顶尖酒店管理和科技校区的教育与研究优势。",
  "verificationClass": "official-clawhub",
  "sourceMappings": [
    "clawhub:cornell-university"
  ],
  "version": "tier2-auto-v3",
